WHAT IS AN ETON MESS?
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    For those of us who are not cock-eyed optimists an Eton Mess is a
    political 'snafu' headed up by a bunch of Bullingdon Club toffs who
    persuade us to take a referendum on our membership of the European
    Union. Then once we, the ignorati, have made our decision they all
    bail out, leaving us with no idea of what to do or where to go. It
    is rather like General Eisenhower dropping the allied troops on the
    Normandy beaches on D Day and then saying, "Well lads, here we are.
    Berlin is... er... that way. Off you go!"

