DEER PARK SCHOOL PLANNING APPLICATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    We are delighted to announce that a planning application for Deer
    Park School's permanent facilities has been submitted to the
    Borough of Richmond. As part of a wider development lead by family
    supermarket Lidl UK at Ryde House, the government have committed
    investment into the future pupils at Deer Park School with this
    exciting mixed use development. It will provide a wonderful
    facility for pupils to learn with the best teachers, enjoy their
    school days and succeed in an environment that enables a love
    for learning.

